trans-unit.source: Specifies the painting style applied to multiple <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> objects contained in a form.
trans-unit.target: Itt adható meg több alkalmazott kifestési stílus <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref> űrlap tartalmazott objektumokat.

trans-unit.source: The ToolStripManagerRenderMode is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager> class and sets the painting style for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> objects that have their <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property set to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderMode?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: A ToolStripManagerRenderMode használják az <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager>osztály és beállítása a kifestési <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>azok <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderMode?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderMode?displayProperty=fullName> tulajdonsággal</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> rendelkező</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> objektumok stílus</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager>

trans-unit.source: You cannot explicitly set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to Custom, however the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is returned Custom when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is set to an extension of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer> class that is not <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>.
trans-unit.target: Explicit módon nem lehet beállítani a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>az egyéni, azonban a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egyéni visszaadott amikor <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName>értéke a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer>nem <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer>vagy <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer> osztály</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer> kiterjesztése</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer"></xref> other than <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Azt jelzi, használatát egy <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer"> </xref> eltérő <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"> </xref> vagy <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"></xref> to paint.
trans-unit.target: Azt jelzi, használatát egy <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"> </xref> festeni kíván.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the use of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer"></xref> to paint.
